  "extensions": {
    "gnn_section": "ActInfPOMDP",
    "footer": "T-Maze Epistemic Foraging Agent v1 - GNN Representation.\nDemonstrates the natural exploration-exploitation trade-off in Active Inference.\nAgent visits cue location to reduce uncertainty before committing to reward arm.\nClassic paradigm from Friston et al. Active Inference literature.",
